name: The Letter
description:
A handwritten letter from your old friend, Peregrine Berlin. 

As their trusted friend, Peregrine has asked for your help. Please come to The House of Ethereal Thought (@House_Ethereal on Twitter) and find Nautilus. 

Many mysteries and discoveries await to those who are granted permission to enter the house. Maybe you’ll be one of the lucky guests. Best keep this letter safe.
